Titolo: Dracula Twins

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Dracula Twins is a platform game developed by Legendo Entertainment and Nerlaska Studio. It was released for Microsoft Windows in October 2006. The single-player game is presented through a third-person perspective. The player controls Drac and Dracana, the twin children of the vampire Count Dracula. The twins have their own special abilities, and earn magic points to cast spells to defeat enemies. The game received generally positive reviews from critics. It received a sequel for iOS in November 2013, with another currently in development for Apple TV, Windows, Nintendo Switch, and Xbox One.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
